text:
Annalise Braakensiek (9 December 1972 – 6 January 2019) was an Australian model, actress, and television presenter. She was born in Sydney. She was known for her role as Claudia Macpherson in the 2000 television series "Pizza" and on the 2003 movie "Fat Pizza".
Braakensiek was found dead in her Sydney apartment on 6 January 2019 at the age of 46.
